{"tid":1785837,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Facebook 更新快捷 Hide Post 功能跟隨每個帖文","createTime":"2019-12-16T16:35:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T16:55:04.000Z","uid":36073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d3a6cc7391e5f9c6f927d02282ae08aacb379508","tid":1785837,"uid":36073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:35:35.000Z","msg":"現在 Facebook 網頁版更新了，可以將 Hide Post 功能帶到你的 News Feed 的每一個帖文。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MOqSx4y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMOqSx4y.png&h=3f72d745&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LQ4v4bw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLQ4v4bw.png&h=23d3b2cc&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LdfZXwf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLdfZXwf.png&h=f8dee706&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n此功能也可應用在廣告上。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d5JwODx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd5JwODx.png&h=39337e2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過，也有些廣告沒有這個按鈕，可能是沒朋友 Like 的專頁就不會有。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J4YMCxD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ4YMCxD.png&h=53423319&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當你進入了專頁看，這功能就會消失。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QhVjc7K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQhVjc7K.png&h=a39d629d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後，Hide Post 那麼快捷，或許方便了你過濾不想看到的資訊。不過，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">你準備好了進入 Facebook 給你的同溫層效應嗎？</span></strong>"},{"pid":"411dd587809639b01f1177889293b2150f7739c1","tid":1785837,"uid":112622,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:42:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3ed111447cf8948d9c3d448d20934402683adb2b","tid":1785837,"uid":36073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"411dd587809639b01f1177889293b2150f7739c1","tid":1